## [0.3.0] - 2025-11-10

### Summary
Sprint 1 - IndexedDB migration complete. Added quota monitoring, migration UI, storage capacity increased to 50GB+.

### Added
- **Quota Monitoring:**
  - `getQuota()` - Returns storage usage, quota, percent used
  - `formatBytes()` - Human-readable format (KB, MB, GB, TB)
  - `isStorageNearlyFull()` - Warning threshold at 80%

- **Migration Service:**
  - src/services/storageMigration.ts (NEW, 154 lines)
  - `needsMigration()` - Detects unmigrated localStorage data
  - `migrateAllData()` - Idempotent migration function
  - `getMigrationStatus()` - Returns completion status

- **Storage UI:**
  - Settings → Advanced tab enhancements
  - Color-coded progress bar (green/yellow/red)
  - Storage usage display
  - Warning banner when >80%
  - Migration UI with detailed results

- **Documentation:**
  - docs/user/storage_migration.md (NEW, 430+ lines)
  - Covers migration process, safety, troubleshooting, FAQ

### Changed
- **Storage Capacity:** 5-10MB (localStorage) → 50GB+ (IndexedDB)
- **Migration:** Auto-migration from localStorage → IndexedDB on first read
- **All Zustand stores:** Now use IndexedDB via `createSyncedStorage()`

### Technical
- Files: src/services/indexedDB.ts (+61 lines), Settings.tsx (+159, -12 lines)
- Time: 8 hours (vs 16-24h estimated)
- Result: Foundation for Notes MVP (no storage limit)

